data.description: ***PRICE ADJUSTMENT***    NO HOA! Less than 10 minutes to UNR or downtown! This home has been well maintained and it shows. Master bedroom is bright and open with a great walk-in closet. Updated flooring installed throughout home, landscaping, and exterior paint in 2019. New central air and water heater 2022. Full bedroom and bathroom located on 1st floor. RV parking!!!  Backyard is spacious with a basketball pad, cement patio, and a flourishing cherry tree!   Assumable FHA Loan!
